===Phrase===
屌你老母 (diú leí loú moú)

#{{vulgar slang}} It literally means "fuck your mother", but is usually translated as "fuck you". This phrase may vary in form, but is usually related to sexual intercourse. The Mandarin equivalent would be [[操你妈]] (cào nĭ mā).

